task.summary: Install cron before cloudwatch and use centos 6 instead of 7.
Added some more dependencies to docker build.
Introduced the flowtree_executor which will run operators from airflow in the FlowTree sandbox.
Working towards a docker image that can actually run the flow tree executor.
Purged the init script of msched-specific code.
Some improvements to the handling of the default job factory, which for some reason was excluded from putting jobs into the pool. Also a lot of maven library files.
Removed archiva, as we now have a real instance in the cloud.
Updated Dockerfile to reflect new airflow design.
Working towards running airflow on flowtree.
Working towards a stable docker image for flowtree.
Use postgres for our airflow database.
